11 (5) a definition of the term “New Americans” for the purposes of an
12 Office of New Americans.
13 (d) The Committee may create subcommittees, with duties and leadership
14 to be assigned by the Chair.
15 (e) Assistance. The Committee shall have the administrative, technical,
16 and legal assistance of the Agency of Human Services.
17 (f) Date of Report. On or before September 1, 2026, the Committee shall
18 submit the written report required by subsection (c) of this section.
19 (g) Meetings.
20 (1) The Chair shall call the first meeting of the Committee to occur on
21 or before September 1, 2025.
